{"tid":589951,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"每段戀愛 都會認錯人 單戀的冠軍","createTime":"2018-03-12T08:11:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-13T16:12:45.000Z","uid":135488,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b8bbf350e68b190afe7562353fedf98f024a1c14","tid":589951,"uid":135488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T08:11:14.000Z","msg":"每段戀愛 都會認錯人 我是單戀的冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係單戀唔係暗戀啊屌你地 暗戀係佢唔知你鍾意佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而單戀係被拒絕後都仲好鍾意佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇同路人 你地點走出陰霾 有嘅可以分享一下<br />\n<br />\n鍾意可以作曬成首佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85bb2f9a0a34a33d95bda5a3e0f7806c929581e2","tid":589951,"uid":21423,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T08:16:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5c34e604806e95a33b8001b6c9fa0981c67680f6","tid":589951,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85bb2f9a0a34a33d95bda5a3e0f7806c929581e2","tid":589951,"uid":21423,"like":27,"dislike":1,"